<title>rby llṣlb ạ̉nt srt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 rby llṣlb ạ̉nt srt wḥdk tḥml ạlậtẖạm
 lys mn ḥwlk ṣdyq trkt fy ẓlạm tạm
 yạ rb wạ̹lhy ḥbk ạlmtnạhy dʿạk llnzwl wqbwl ạlậlạm
 ạ̉yạ rby yswʿy yạ ạ̹lh ạlṣlyb qd msḥt dmwʿy ḥạnyạ yạ ḥbyb
 qṭrạt dmạk blsm lljrạḥ bk ykẖtfy ḥzny wbkạỷy ạlnwạḥ
 jỷt mtẖqlạ bạldẖnb ʿyny ạ̉ʿyạhạ ạlbkạʾ
 jỷt rfʿt ʿny dẖnby rạfʿạ nfsy llsmạʾ
 yạ rby wạ̹lhy ḥbk ạlmtnạhy whbtny ạlḥyạẗ wạlnjạẗ wạlhnạʾ
 ạ̉yạ fạdy ḥyạty yạ rjạʾ ạlkẖṭạẗ fyk rby njạty mn qṣạṣ ạlạ̹lh
 ạ̉hdyk fy ṣlạty kl mjd wjạh lk wḥdk ậty fy ṣlạty wạlḥyạẗ</lyrics>
</song>